员、干部工作作风不实、履职不力，存在失管失察、失职失责等行为。我们将以零容忍的态度坚决查处整治，汲取教训、引以为戒，深入践行以人民为中心的发展思想和人民至上理念，主动接受社会监督，进一步加强基层组织建设，持续深化干部队伍作风建设，不断提升公共服务和社会治理效能，不断提升人民群众的获得感、幸福感、安全感。广西通报“容县梁二夫妇生育15孩”有关问题调查处理情况"},"attached_info":"Cj4IpL7VqNn5oppTEAMaCDc4NTI0MTU4IIbJ3JEGMAA4V0Aacgk1MjMwOTIxNTd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"147 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-30d8ef9c701e80136f5f6d18640b96d7_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"27_1647789061.6224601","card_id":"Q_522250404","target":{"id":522250404,"title":"在国企工作工资低，周末双休，但是太压抑，怎么办？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/522250404","type":"question","created":1647407520,"answer_count":140,"follower_count":263,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[6391,9276,54520,153611,165829],"comment_count":7,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8IpL7VqNn5oppTEAMaCDc4MzM3NTcwIKDjxZEGMAc4hwJAG3IJNTIyMjUwNDA0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"141 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"28_1647789061.6228127","card_id":"Q_512241162","target":{"id":512241162,"title":"最近看见了哪些让你破防的句子？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/512241162","type":"question","created":1642523373,"answer_count":113,"follower_count":609,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[410903],"comment_count":1,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8IpL7VqNn5oppTEAMaCDc2MTEzMDE3IO3Vm48GMAE44QRAHHIJNTEyMjQxMTYyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"123 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-7d24f71c9a30df2191ac35537d0bf823_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_